dc_description_s: Surrounded by 19 vignettes, mostly commercial buildings. "Explanatory" key to 88 places in bottom margin. "This birds eye view of Tacoma is issued by Geo. W. Traver ... "at top center. "Litho "Elliott Pub. Co." 120 Sutter St. S.F." 1 view; 32 x 73 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S.
